channel.title: Insanity X
channel.description: Alright well I am using Insanity X server+client and I can get on it but when I change the character rights to 3 and I try to spawn somthing it says "You're not authorized enough to do this" even though im owner? It also will not let me teleport if i do "::tele 1 1" or any cords. Does anyone know how i can fix this?

item.title: Insanity X
item.dc:creator: @owwch_u_died owwch u died
item.description:
@owwch_u_died wrote:

Lookup “pickup” or “watever your command is” in your client find that command, and make sure that it doesnt have like:

if (username.IgnoresEquals(blah blah blah) a certain name.

If it does have that, take out the name and add yours or make the rights (>2) or watever you’d like. =P
